How do the children get involved? How involved are they?\

\b0 The children use to be tied to a string and walk across the ice to pull the net up (to harvest the fish) and then walk the other direction to reset the gill net.\

\b \
Are the children taught methods in fishing?\

\b0 If the children saw what was being practiced, they would take more interest in the traditional way of life. They are currently being distracted by media and electronics.\
